name: RUMAH GADANG - WEST SUMATRA TRADITIONAL HOUSE (INDONESIA)
description:
Rumah Gadang is the name for the Minangkabau traditional house which is a traditional house and is often found in West Sumatra, Indonesia. This house is also called by another name by the local community by the name of Rumah Bagonjong or some also call it by the name of Rumah Baanjuang.
